"Jeong", "role": "饰：Goon-bong''s daughter", "image": "https://p0.meituan.net/movie/ab0eda0dcbf28455e5e18da6571b19fe6071.jpg@128w_170h_1e_1c"}, {"name": "罗美兰", "role": "饰：Nurse", "image": "https://p1.meituan.net/movie/e71e462699603fa1179e0c9f7554b6fa37669.jpg@128w_170h_1e_1c"}, {"name": "金香奇", "role": "饰：Street light girl", "image": "https://p1.meituan.net/movie/b00de16699ba3a7dc4bdd83dcf28839e15026.jpg@128w_170h_1e_1c"}, {"name": "李相勋", "role": "饰：Deok-bae (as Sang-hun Lee)", "image": "https://p0.meituan.net/movie/dc2f571e437254835d8d4af5b53595e328936.jpg@128w_170h_1e_1c"}, {"name": "李俊赫", "role": "饰：Photographer (as Joon Hyuk Lee)", "image": "https://p0.meituan.net/movie/4ef01387d83e676f60ec1db455246e1036622.jpg@128w_170h_1e_1c"}]', 9.1, '2026-04-24 03:07:06.443382', '2026-04-24 03:07:06.443382', '["https://p0.meituan.net/movie/4d3f9c09a5c692896893d639ba792567386076.jpg@106w_106h_1e_1c", "https://p0.meituan.net/movie/f14118d18f2bc01f607eacae616e19e8237743.jpg@106w_106h_1e_1c", "https://p1.meituan.net/movie/b958476c444c45ae10cf0c06347c6d58313480.jpg@106w_106h_1e_1c", "https://p1.meituan.net/movie/2c9b9abcec84d7bbfe96fa70de567291397390.jpg@106w_106h_1e_1c", "https://p0.meituan.net/movie/45dd145d66528529486b46ea4968ba9c377843.jpg@106w_106h_1e_1c", "https://p0.meituan.net/movie/cd294d0b71638140e86550fc733599f7117975.jpg@106w_106h_1e_1c", "https://p0.meituan.net/movie/c9a4f37a57221f45a6bff6b53de3b75b76278.jpg@106w_106h_1e_1c", "https://p1.meituan.net/movie/92d97a264eab7921d2d08189096a5245113073.jpg@106w_106h_1e_1c", "https://p0.meituan.net/movie/a8e58c6ec39a92ab93d7bafa3c387a5d30011.jpg@106w_106h_1e_1c", "https://p0.meituan.net/movie/d678725b9186f14d7bae0d6708fc6e92147918.jpg@106w_106h_1e_1c", "https://p0.meituan.net/movie/6e7b0377d1419233e28c75af20f9db7578295.jpg@106w_106h_1e_1c", "https://p0.meituan.net/movie/d7aa183368be2e432e0b993950976b50100448.jpg@106w_106h_1e_1c", "https://p1.meituan.net/movie/c7cdc2c3db55b3f1c273f6df12e5b04683155.jpg@106w_106h_1e_1c", "https://p